Description: Easy to use and fast desktop frontend for logging hours in Jira
  Friendly and fast frontend for logging hours in Jira. Notable features include:
  - Rapid time logging via calendar-style blocks
  - Fast issue search end reuse of recently used issues
  - A happy color scheme to brighten your day
